{"tid":843680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮檢基明報名參加立會九西補選","createTime":"2018-10-01T10:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T10:59:56.000Z","uid":39521,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b610409052c48cff10c52dec3552e17dd76465b4","tid":843680,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181001/s00001/1538389316887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181001%2Fs00001%2F1538389316887&d=gyT6NCKs291rbtPbCDDifttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=cac54be5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181001%2Fs00001%2F1538389316887&h=89ccaa77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181001/s00001/1538389316887</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會九龍西補選提名期明日展開，已退出民協的馮檢基今年年初曾表明不會再參選，他近日改變口風，稱工黨劉小麗被取消參選資格後，自己會考慮參選。不過，劉小麗尚未報名參選之際，馮檢基今日已向傳媒發出採訪通知，稱會於明日下午3時，報名參加補選。<br />\n<br />\n問及為何在劉小麗確認參選資格前，他仍急於在明日報名參選，馮檢基稱「明日才告訴你們」，強調自己「不是很急，（提名期）明日也開始」。對於𠝹票或收錢參選等指控，馮檢基稱自己未報名時，已經被如此指控，「唔報都畀佢哋話，報咗咪無嘢畀佢哋話」，指有些人不是根據事實評論，而是根據自己想像去作出評論，這些評論是沒有意思。<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗明早11時半將報名參選，至於獲建制派支持的前食衛局政治助理陳凱欣，今午亦向傳媒發採訪通知，稱明早11時將舉行分享會，交代參選與否的「最新決定」。據了解，陳凱欣屆時將正式宣布參選。<br />\n<br />\n=========<br />\n<br />\n雲加都退馮檢基仲未退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38164dc2546f37b7222633c9e372f6979284fb7","tid":843680,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"得閒做下義工好過啦 何必衝出黎柒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc16fcb4900739db78dfb81ec009f58ebc5c0ae","tid":843680,"uid":29804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"好 撐"},{"pid":"025d7eb65efd3f7473aca376ce844e06ed52bc80","tid":843680,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"希望一道雷劈撚死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86522694e5ed87ad609de3d646a8231453d79fae","tid":843680,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"小麗老母 gg 了"},{"pid":"df69ed21bb680e745ecfdee1717ffddccdad46a6","tid":843680,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"基哥喺論壇度數臭大台霸權就精彩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53d512f2db70003af35223d4575c112456460e2","tid":843680,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"加埋香港共產黨小麗老母就玩完"},{"pid":"0f807f90b61f5796acd09197be7538b9c7d3bb57","tid":843680,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"係窮啊,屌你個閪"},{"pid":"659ab921c028c30a646a0147f5e2bba0b0dc0e65","tid":843680,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"𠝹票之王"},{"pid":"fd8031074e37e416dafd5127d5e8640506e75a87","tid":843680,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"政壇ATV"},{"pid":"90d8670ddaf4897f5216bf7489ebb983eae8f63d","tid":843680,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i782.photobucket.com/albums/yy110/johnsonbrown123/fungkk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi782.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fyy110%2Fjohnsonbrown123%2Ffungkk.jpg&h=95716fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴力保皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}